From: Ren Wang <iamwrm@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:24:23 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 10/15] Add built-in Anthropic Claude model catalog

Register pi's adaptive-thinking Claude generation (Opus 4.6-4.8, Sonnet
4.6/5, Fable 5) under anthropic/<id> keys routed to the Anthropic
Messages API with the anthropic_oauth scheme and efforts low through max.
The catalog only appears when ~/.grok/anthropic_auth.json exists and is
inserted before [model.*] overrides so user customization still wins.
